thread.title: Rick

author: Rick
title: Rick
text: I received the first package quickly but it only contained the large company catalogue which made me think they forgot to include the item I purchased. I sent a couple of emails about the missing part which were not returned. Several days later I received the part I ordered. Still don't know if the part was missed in the first package or they always split up the orders and catalogue.
